::Amperion::
       I looks at her quizzically glancing at her wing emblems.  "Bit out of 
place aren't you?"  He then looks confused and glances around rapidly.  "How 
did I know that?  I'm sorry I'm just a bit disoriented.  My name is Amperion. 
 It is my pleasure to make your acquaintance."  He makes a very formal and 
crisp bow.
